ProMED-mail Rapporteur Mary Marshall

[The low number of cases being reported is concerning rather than reassuring, making one suspicious cases are going undetected, especially when there are unidentified chains of transmission. - Mod.LK]

- Fri 11 Jan 2019. Epidemiological situation report, DRC Ministry of Health
[in French, machine trans., abridged, edited]
